OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start in the
OL,6,Feast, otherwise a largely cloudy day
OL,7,Fwith widespread showers, some heavy
OL,8,Fand thundery. Some bright spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping in the afternoon,
OL,10,Fespecially along the North Coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome heavy showers to start
OL,13,Fthe evening but these will slowly die
OL,14,Fout. Further showers will then
OL,15,Fspreading in from the west overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy day with a
OL,18,Ffew showers but becoming drier and
OL,19,Fbrighter during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
