OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,7,FThursday but becoming drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter later. Sunshine and scattered
OL,9,Fshowers on Friday then dry, bright and
OL,10,Fturning warmer on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
